Ace Hardware Reward

Hey, I finally got around to fixing that old bike chain using the tool you recommended. It took a little patience but the chain is running smooth now. I also tried the new coffee blend from the roaster downtown and it's pretty solid. Let me know if you want to grab a cup this weekend. I also finished reading that sci-fi novel you lent me and loved it. The way the author built the world was incredible. I'm planning to start the sequel next week. Hope you're doing well.

 

ACE
Hardware

Ace is the Place with the Helpful Hardware Folks

MEMBERSHIP REWARDS NOTICE

Your $100 Reward + Ring Doorbell Awaits

As a committed Ace customer, your continued loyalty means everything to us. To recognize your support this year, we're delighted to offer you a $100 Thank You Reward along with a Ring Doorbell.

Only available today. Don't miss out.

Member ID: 85902-6156

Loyalty Points: 1,965

Reward Status: Ready to Claim

Join millions of homeowners who trust Ace Hardware for quality products and exceptional service. Your reward is reserved.

Claim Your $100 + Ring Doorbell

