Ace Hardware

I have been meaning to tell you that the hiking trail out near the lake is finally open again. We went last weekend and the views were amazing. The water level is high so the falls are really impressive right now. Also, the little café near the trailhead has a new pastry chef and everything we tried was delicious. Let me know if you want to plan a trip there soon. I can bring the cooler and some snacks. It would be a nice way to spend a Saturday.

